{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"platforms":[{"beta":false,"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"15.0"},{"beta":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"16.0"},{"beta":false,"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"11.0"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents16OUDSCheckboxItemV"},"abstract":[{"text":"Checkbox is a UI element that allows to select multiple options from a set of mutually non exclusive choices.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Checkbox item covers a wider range of contexts by allowing to toggle the visibility of additional text labels and icon assets.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading","text":"Layouts","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","text":"Indicator states","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ Localizable from bundle can also be used","    OUDSCheckboxItem(LocalizedStringKey(\"agree_terms\"), bundle: Bundle.module, isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and a description as helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Bazinga!\", isOn: $isOn, description: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, a description and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"We live in a fabled world\",","                     isOn: $isOn,","                     description: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isReversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"We live in a fabled world\",","                     isOn: $isOn,","                     isError: true,","                     errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                     hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Cocorico !\",","                     isOn: $selection,","                     icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                     flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                     isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"anchor":"Suggestions","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}],"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","level":2},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkboxItem_OrangeCompact"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version","style":"note"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(_:isOn:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem